extends ../ui_layout

block content
  
  .ui.text.container.addBottomMargin
    br
    .ui.raised.segment
      h3.ui.header
        i.book.blue.icon
        .content
          | Learn
      hr
      .ui.basic.segment.removePadding
        .ui.mini.green.right.labeled.icon.button.showLearnSectionButton
          i.down.arrow.icon
          |   Next
      .ui.basic.segment.learnSegment.hidden
        h5.ui.header
          i.arrow.circle.right.blue.icon
          .content.
            Social media can connect people over the Internet. People use social 
            media to share information, their interests, and connect with 
            friends and family. They can also use it to talk to new people and 
            meet new friends!
   
        h5.ui.header
          i.arrow.circle.right.blue.icon
          .content.
            On social media, you may be talking to many different people at the 
            same time. You might not know some of them in real life. Remember to 
            always be careful about the information you share online, especially 
            with people you've never met face-to-face.
        br
        .ui.mini.green.right.labeled.icon.button.showKeyTermsButton
          i.down.arrow.icon
          |   Next
    
    .ui.segment.keyIdeasSegment.hidden
      h3.ui.header
        i.key.blue.icon
        .content Key Ideas
      .sub.header.grayElement 
        i.hand.pointer.icon
        span Click on each word below to learn more
      br   
      .ui.stackable.two.column.grid
        .ui.column
          .ui.raised.segment.keyTerm.voiceover_keyTerm1
            a.ui.blue.ribbon.label.keyTermLabel
                span Audience
            span.hidden.keyTermDefinition
              | Anyone who can see information about you or posted by you online. 
              ul This could include strangers or people you haven't met face-to-face.
        .ui.column
          .ui.raised.segment.keyTerm.voiceover_keyTerm2
            a.ui.blue.ribbon.label.keyTermLabel
                span Private information
            span.hidden.keyTermDefinition 
              | Information about you that can be used to identify you because 
              | it is unique to you.
              ul This can include things like your full name, school, home 
                | address, or phone number.
        
        .ui.column
          .ui.raised.segment.keyTerm.voiceover_keyTerm3
            a.ui.blue.ribbon.label.keyTermLabel
                span Risky
            span.hidden.keyTermDefinition 
              | Potentially harmful to oneâ€™s emotional or physical well-being.
              ul It is risky to share private information online. People could 
                | share it with others or use it to try to trick or scam you.
    
    .ui.warning.message#clickNextWarning
      .header
       | Click "Next"
    .ui.warning.message#clickLabelsWarning
     .header
      | Click on each label to proceed  
    a(href='javascript:void(0);', onclick='javascript:clickGotIt();')
      .ui.labeled.icon.button
          i.rocket.icon
          |   Got it!
          
